OL,3,CCardiff University job cuts could
OL,4,C'threaten supply of nurses'
OL,6,FJob cuts at Cardiff University could
OL,7,Fthreaten the supply of nurses across
OL,8,FWales according to a union leader.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday the Vice Chancellor of the
OL,11,Funiversity announced that "difficult
OL,12,Fdecisions" had to be taken which could
OL,13,Fsee up to 400 roles going and nursing
OL,14,Fcourses being axed.
OL,16,FProfessor Wendy Larner said "we need
OL,17,Fto take difficult decisions to realise
OL,18,Four ambitions to enhance our education
OL,19,Fand research, and improve the staff
OL,20,Fand student experience.''
