OL,3,CCardiff University job cuts could
OL,4,C'threaten supply of nurses'
OL,6,FShe said the proposals, now under a 90
OL,7,Fday consultation, could see the
OL,8,Funiversity stopping courses in Ancient
OL,9,FHistory, Modern Languages and
OL,10,FTranslation, Music, Religion and
OL,11,FNursing.
OL,13,FNow the Royal College of Nursing Wales
OL,14,Fsays the changes were 'worrying'.
OL,16,FIts Executive Director, Helen Whyley,
OL,17,Fsaid she was concerned the proposal
OL,18,Fcomes at a time when Wales faces a
OL,19,Fsevere nursing shortage.
