OL,3,CCardiff University job cuts could
OL,4,C'threaten supply of nurses'
OL,6,F"Although the University has assured
OL,7,Fme that it is committed to honour
OL,8,Fplaces in this year's nursing
OL,9,Fprogrammes, the proposed closure of
OL,10,Fsuch a prestigious institution
OL,11,Fprogramme will have a significant
OL,12,Fimpact on the future of nursing in
OL,13,FWales.
OL,15,F"Its School of Nursing has a long-
OL,16,Fstanding reputation for excellence
OL,17,Fproducing highly skilled,
OL,18,Fcompassionate nurses who have gone on
OL,19,Fto serve communities locally and
OL,20,Facross Wales" she said.
