OL,3,CCardiff University job cuts could
OL,4,C'threaten supply of nurses'
OL,6,FMs Whyley warned it could threaten the
OL,7,F'pipeline' of registered nurses into
OL,8,Fhealth boards in south Wales.
OL,10,F''The closure of these programmes
OL,11,Fwould be a huge disappointment for the
OL,12,Fprofession, local communities, and
OL,13,FWales. RCN Wales will be responding to
OL,14,Fthe consultation'' she added.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Secretary Jo Stevens was
OL,17,Fchallenged about the job losses during
OL,18,Fthis week's Welsh Questions by Plaid
OL,19,FCymru MP Liz Saville Roberts who
OL,20,Fcalled it an "education disaster
OL,21,Fplaying out in real time."
