OL,4,C'threaten supply of nurses'
OL,6,FMs Saville Roberts went on to ask the
OL,7,FSecretary of State: "Will the
OL,8,Fgovernment scrap National Insurance
OL,9,Fhikes to ease the strain of
OL,10,Funiversities?"
OL,12,FIn response, Ms Stevens said that "the
OL,13,Fpotential job losses at Cardiff
OL,14,FUniversity are deeply concerning, and
OL,15,FI know they will come as a significant
OL,16,Fblow to university staff and their
OL,17,Ffamilies.
