OL,6,F"I hope sufficient volunteers through
OL,7,Fa voluntary redundancy program will
OL,8,Fcome forward and be achieved in order
OL,9,Fto avoid any compulsory redundancies,
OL,10,Fand that support will be provided to
OL,11,Fthose impacted.
OL,13,F"But what she will know is that the
OL,14,Flast 14 years of conservative policies
OL,15,Fhave seen our university sector across
OL,16,Fthe United Kingdom decimated."
OL,18,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,19,F"We understand the serious concern
OL,20,FCardiff University's announcement will
OL,21,Fcause for people affected.
