OL,3,CCardiff University job cuts could
OL,4,C'threaten supply of nurses'
OL,6,F"Universities across the UK are facing
OL,7,Fa challenging financial period due to
OL,8,Fa range of factors and we expect all
OL,9,Finstitutions to work with trade
OL,10,Funions, staff and students on any
OL,11,Fproposals.
OL,13,F"Universities are independent
OL,14,Finstitutions, but we are very
OL,15,Fdisappointed that nursing courses form
OL,16,Fpart of these proposals and we are
OL,17,Fworking urgently with HEIW to ensure
OL,18,Fwe train the same number of nurses in
OL,19,FWales."
